{"solution": "A streamlined, Airtable-based system that lets your team leverage their human capital where it matters most: steering the ship. Your team will add industry search terms (i.e C++ developer) using a simple form, and it'll trigger an outreach workflow.

The workflow will automatically scrape LinkedIn for jobs that have been posted for that position or for people with that role, funnel that data into an enrichment & deliverability pipeline (DropContact, Neverbounce, etc), and begin a coordinated email outreach sequence to push interested candidates to Calendly. 

Reply categorization will be done automatically by AI (GPT-4), and your team will only be alerted when a positive outcome is reached (i.e meeting booked), or if a situation arises that the system doesn't yet know how to deal with - in which case the situation would be added to the categorization system so it handles it effectively in the future.", "roughTimetable":"3 weeks"}
